      "content": "it's like i'm just going through the motions of a person who doesn't exist anymore. i make coffee, i go to work, i come home... but i'm just a shell. he was the part of me that actually felt alive. without him, i'm just waiting for something that's never coming back. it feels so pointless to just keep pretending.",
